const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What’s included in a Home Detailing service?",
    answer: "Our Home Detailing service is like a luxury detail for your home. It includes:\n\n• Whole-Home Care: Deep dusting and polishing of baseboards, trim, vents, doors, and molding. Cleaning of air vents, light switches, and outlet covers.\n• Kitchen Detail: Degreasing and polishing of exterior appliances, microwave interior, and deep scrubbing of countertops and backsplash.\n• Bathroom Refresh: Deep removal of soap scum, hard water stains, and buildup; polishing fixtures and disinfecting all surfaces.\n• Floors & Finishes: Edge-to-edge vacuuming and professional mopping with specialized floor-care products.\n\nThis service is designed to restore brilliance and reach the hidden corners that standard cleaning might miss."
