  {
    question: "How is Home Detailing different from Deep Cleaning?",
    answer: "Deep Cleaning is a standard top-to-bottom reset focusing on dirt removal. Home Detailing goes a step further by including specialized polishing, precision dusting of architectural details (like molding and vents), and a more exhaustive focus on high-touch surfaces and restorative finishes to make your home feel brand-new."
